# Vendor phone test — always show QR

When the task touches **vendor receive**, **PIN gate**, `/#/receive`, **iPhone/Safari vendor testing**, or Dan should verify on a physical phone:

**Canonical vendor UI:** `ReceivingPage` at `/#/receive` only. `appSettings.vendorDeliveryMode` toggles exception-only Delivered hub vs legacy full check-in on the **same page**. Legacy `/#/` and `/#/checkin/:id` redirect to receive — do not rebuild separate vendor UIs.

1. **Open** the demo QR page in Glass/browser:
   `https://lgarage.github.io/stageverify/#/demo/vendor-scan`
   (or `npm run open:vendor-demo-qr` on Windows)
2. **Include in the reply** — link, PIN `1234`, and a Playwright screenshot of that page saved to `screenshots/vendor-demo/qr-for-phone.png` (gitignored; for Dan to scan from chat).
3. **Direct link fallback:** `https://lgarage.github.io/stageverify/#/receive?id=delivery-demo-vendor-1`

Do not declare vendor/iPhone work "ready for Dan" without step 2 in the same reply.
